rows.label: tev001411_MSG0010
rows.name:
Outta the frying pan, and straight into the
damned fire. Doesn't look like we'll be
getting a beach vacation anytime soon...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001411_MSG0020
rows.name:
How are you holding up, though?
Do you need any help? Just say the word,
and I'm with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001411_MSG0050
rows.name:
There we go! All right, I've got your back.
Let's hit the road![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001411_MSG0080
rows.name:
I see. Well, you keep hanging in there,
okay? I'll do what I can as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001411_MSG0090
rows.name:
A contest for survival, huh...?
If he's so certain of winning this thing,
then he's underestimating us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001411_MSG0100
rows.name:
He thinks he's got us licked, but we've
been fighting for our survival every damn
day, ever since we left Earth behind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001411_MSG0110
rows.name:
Let's show the bastard just exactly
how wrong he is, shall we?[ST:wait ]
